# Book controller requests example #

### Get request to book controller return list of books
GET http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/books
Accept: application/json

### Post request to book controller return created book
POST http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/books
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "textfield",
  "author": "textfield"
}

### Get request to book controller, return book by id
GET http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/books/1
Accept: application/json

### Get request to book controller, return list of books by reader id
GET http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/books/1/readers
Accept: application/json

# Reader controller requests example #

### Get request to reader controller return list of readers
