# Borrow controller requests example #

### Get request to borrow controller return list of borrows
GET http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/borrows
Accept: application/json


### Get request to borrow controller return Borrow object
POST http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/borrows?readerId=3&bookId=4
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


### Get request to borrow controller return Http status code
DELETE http://localhost:8081/bookslib/api/v1/library/borrows?readerId=3&bookId=4
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded


